lead_paragraph: The National Football League's annual exhibition of all-stars, the Pro Bowl, will move from its long-time home in Hawaii to Orlando for next year, the league announced on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: 2017 Pro Bowl to Be Played in Orlando
